Flash Before My Eyes - Whispers From The World 2014 ak

Flash Before My Eyes is a 5 piece progressive/metalcore band based in Rome, Italy.
We have shared the stage with bands like Texas In July,Salt The Wound,War From a Harlots Mouth,Here Comes The Kraken,Arsonists Get All The Girls ,A Plea For Purging,Awaken Demons,Helia,etc..
Our debut album "Whispers From The World" is available now
